video_title: This is Why You Should Prioritize Other People
transcript:
last thing that we're going to talk a
little bit about is also something that
I hear a lot from hustle culture which
is putting yourself first so a lot of
people out there will sort of say that
you know this is a dog eat dog world and
that if you want to get ahead in life
you've got to prioritize yourself no
one's going to look out for you so you
got to look out for yourself in my
experience that's actually not the case
where what I've really found is that
prioritizing other people in a lot of
situations is actually the best thing in
terms of your productivity and success
if you're always looking out for
yourself and you're kind of number one
in every situation then other people are
going to start stop looking out for you
and if other people stop looking out for
you that's going to create all kinds of
problems in terms of lack of
professional opportunities in terms of
people not asking you for help in terms
of all kinds of things
